Usage:

1. Create monitor device mon0
2. insmod wifi-statistics.ko 
3. cat /sys/kernel/debug/wifi_statistics/stats 

Optional:
echo "read" > /sys/kernel/debug/wifi_statistics/mode
or
echo "reset" > /sys/kernel/debug/wifi_statistics/mode

The reset mode is similar to the read mode, delets all
stations from the internal database when reading.
In read mode, the internal database is not modified.
